tdout/mutable tables instead of immutable SIEM collectors.\n   * **Non-Hardened Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)**: simulated frontend roles, needing a rigorous backend BOLA/privilege escalation audit.\n   * **Absence of File Scanning & Malware Filtering**: mocked document uploads bypass physical malware scanning.\n   * **Zero Payment Compliance Integration**: billing and invoice values computed dynamically from local db seed templates without PCI-DSS audits.\n3. **Phase 6 Enterprise Security Hardening Roadmap:**\n   * Migrating to **Production-Grade Persistence Engine** (AWS Aurora Serverless v2 PostgreSQL"}}
